{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":550850,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"过A’做cd平行线\n对B'和其余三个点同样操作\n得到一个与原来五边形位似得五边形\n这个新的五边形比A’B’C’D’E’周长大\n但是可以说明它的周长成常数倍递减\n然后原来的五边形永远在这个新的更大的五边形里面\n而这类新的五边形收敛于一点\n所以okk啦","timestamp":1605273041,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":550859,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"做出一点让步就搞定","timestamp":1605273190,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":551120,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"谢谢，我试一下(如果这个对，应该也要倒倒比例才能出来吧,因为五条边相对平行的五边形一般情况下应该不位似）","timestamp":1605276542,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":551173,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"快进到压缩映射原理","timestamp":1605277318,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":551232,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 我只能证明面积被压缩😂 ","timestamp":1605277908,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":551291,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"快进到五点共圆","timestamp":1605278334,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":551576,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{"h":482,"w":800},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 你的claim应该是有问题的","timestamp":1605282042,"type":"image","url":"kp/kp72332shfgz7vudv37tvrgxdpspyrsj.jpeg"},{"cid":551623,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":114859,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"感觉能不能作个线性映射之类的","timestamp":1605282692,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":551624,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","per